Keeping it short and sweet. June is men’s mental health awareness. Too often we neglect our own mental health in fear of what others will think of us. (Especially as a creative person) But at the end of the day your own mind and thoughts are what matters the most. Life changes, you have wins and you have losses. Reflect on the past But focus on the things in life you can control and your life will change in ways you never though we’re possible. improve your self everyday, and remember it’s ok to not be ok. take some time get out of your head and back into your life. #mentalhealthawareness #timetotakeaction

Some of it cost a lot but Camera equipment doesn’t have to be expensive I found this opteka lens for $89 on Amazon and it has quickly become one of my favorite lenses to use 🎥 . As a skater a fish eye has always been an staple when filming, there’s just something about being able to just hit record and capture everything and more in view. #sony #fisheye #skateboarding #cameragear
